":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"d6e858b5725bce084458110e2ad5bc89e1882fba","tid":854994,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"王騎你真係燈燈地 有時講少兩句好"},{"pid":"f896cff16a1b178713697b2e0764d47a5b57ea92","tid":854994,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"王大將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47798b5974e25c59085b1c13bcece8e2b8d10b40","tid":854994,"uid":15862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反浚朗大將軍"},{"pid":"da233a0d5349d8d2d8583f82e17c909f0b751937","tid":854994,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"燈到牙俊退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b826c9ba11cdb641be2585d516683060c50bd34","tid":854994,"uid":68794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:51:17.000Z","msg":"大將!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d3f144930c93aaf2123fc0705873a73f9bdd66","tid":854994,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"【英國直擊．戴偉浚】專訪浚仔私人教練：C朗苦練故事影響全國<br />\n<br />\n過去一年，戴偉浚主要到位於Wythenshawe的Manchester Enterprise Academy作一對一訓練。舉辦這間學院的為現職曼城青年球探的卡路士洛卡（Carlos Roca），這名前職業球員製定訓練內容，再由旗下助教執行，其對象主要是4至10歲，辦學3年有近500名學生，除了英國足球文化深厚外，亦與C朗有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「C朗將整個環境改變，來到曼聯後苦練的故事被廣泛報道後，英國人知道他的成功全因做很多私人訓練，過去亦有學者分析他10年來的成長，更令英國人感到，只要投放更多時間，自然有更好的成績。」"},{"pid":"d906a1fedc4e6a0a865474f9f993d02f8e4cfd11","tid":854994,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}